    "key": "533692d499c255ea648e6427334318eb5886746f12fa9a29e7fcc941db86f9b3",
    "original": " no longer has ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "_s + \" no longer has \" + this.m.Name"
  },
  {
    "key": "a0a4d5a0a49ec1f86c5178602a8c9170b39450f5963c5deb7da8a5d049c83ed6",
    "original": " now has ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "_s + \" now has \" + this.m.Name"
  },
  {
    "key": "20f60ccd975b7b0e698347f74584db61f7dff975ff164ebf3edde325a20bd100",
    "original": "Ambushed Trade Routes",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Name = \"Ambushed Trade Routes\""
  },
  {
    "key": "b526d62d540949c435d4c8dd2aec357ce055e2487c418db9bb742ae06ddad6b1",
    "original": "Brigands and raiders are the bane of us traveling merchants! An old friend of mine got ambushed, robbed and beaten just outside of %settlement%!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "843efa8ff7baaf28b68445d8b6ba4985acf855d5c1ca02e4e3aec6ac2d85f62b",
    "original": "If you have any valuables on you, stay away from %settlement%. The place is scourged by cutthroats, bandits and highwaymen!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "bdf6c4c5fe869c4a2d342ce312e61854ec9cca04948553ef53a4694dd047037c",
    "original": "The guardsmen are doing what they can, but these brigands just move on to the next town and waylay traders on the road. They're said to lurk around %settlement% now!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "1d1bc5aff6278f9601d4f8101dd4aded9e3f6e9aaf0d0e99a5dc40646ff37e80",
    "original": "The roads leading here are unsafe of late, and many a caravan has been ambushed and plundered. With little successful trade, the selection of goods is lower and the prices higher.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Description = \"The roads leading here are unsafe of late, and many a caravan has been ambushed and plundered. With little successful trade, the selection of goods is lower and the prices higher.\""
  }
]